Definition: a figure of speech in which an expression is used to refer to something that it does not literally denote in order to suggest a similarity
Synonyms: adj, all, figurative, metaphoric, metaphorical, trope, a, figure, of, speech, in, which, an, expression, is, used, to, refer, something, that, it, does, not, literally, denote, order, suggest, similarity
Category: noun.communication
